name: $contentType
desc: Returns: The mime type to send the payload in - either application/fhir+xml, or application/fhir+json. The MIME types "text/plain" and "text/html" may also be used for Email subscriptions.

pvardefs.name: pValue
pvardefs.desc: The mime type to send the payload in - either application/fhir+xml, or application/fhir+json. The MIME types "text/plain" and "text/html" may also be used for Email subscriptions.

name: $content
desc: Returns: How much of the resource content to deliver in the notification payload. The choices are an empty payload, only the resource id, or the full resource content.
